## Strategy: How to Get to 10+
1. Faster alignment cycling: reduce travel time between junctions (shorter paths)
2. More hearts per batch: already scaling 3→4→5→6, could increase further
3. Better chain building: align junctions that create chains toward more reachable junctions
4. Wipeout mitigation: seed 0 scored 0.00 — fixing wipeouts would boost avg significantly
5. Running 10-seed test (seeds 0-9) for reliable average
